uts, sugar, nonfat milk, dextrose, corn syrup solids \u2013 and vegetable oil, consisting of a mix of palm, palm kernel, shea, sunflower and safflower oils.In addition to the classic Reese\u2019s cups, the white version comes in egg form for Easter and as unwrapped minis.\u00a0\u00a0Editor's Note: This story has been updated with comments from the confectioner and the law firm.\u200b\n",
